%description
Adobe Utopia 100dpi bitmap font.

This package includes Unicode font as well as in ISO-8859-1,
ISO-8859-2, ISO-8859-3, ISO-8859-4, ISO-8859-9, ISO-8859-10,
ISO-8859-13, ISO-8859-14 and ISO-8859-15 encodings.

